Ace actress, Folake Aremu, popularly known as Orisabunmi has just been reported dead. The announcement of her demise came via the Nollywood Circle@nollycircle tweeter handle Wednesday morning. ” We have just received the news of the demise of Veteran Actress, Orisabunmi. May her soul rest in Peace. Folake Aremu popularly known as Orisabunmi has been a phenomenal part of the film industry for more than four decades. She starred in productions including Arelu, Yanponyanrin”; the tweet reads. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! 